  "id": "php/syntax",
  "contentHtml": "<h1>Basic Syntax</h1>\n<p>Can be placed anywhere in a document.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Script starts with <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math><semantics><mrow><mo>&#x3C;</mo><mo>?</mo><mi>p</mi><mi>h</mi><mi>p</mi></mrow><annotation>&#x3C;?php</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">&#x3C;</span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\"></span><span class=\"mclose\">?</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">p</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">h</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">p</span></span></span></span> and ends with <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math><semantics><mrow><mo>?</mo><mo>></mo></mrow><annotation>?></annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\"></span><span class=\"mclose\">?</span><span class=\"mspace\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">></span></span></span></span></li>\n<li>Extension is .php</li>\n<li>Contains HTML tags, and some scripting code.</li>\n<li>PHP statements end with a ;</li>\n</ul>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs language-html\"><span class=\"hljs-meta\">&#x3C;!DOCTYPE <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">html</span>></span>\n<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&#x3C;<span class=\"hljs-name\">html</span>></span>\n\n<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&#x3C;<span class=\"hljs-name\">body</span>></span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&#x3C;<span class=\"hljs-name\">h1</span>></span> Tristan's PHP Page! <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&#x3C;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">h1</span>></span>\n\n    <span class=\"hljs-meta\">&#x3C;?php\n        echo \"Hello world!\";\n    ?></span>\n<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&#x3C;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">body</span>></span>\n\n<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&#x3C;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">html</span>></span>\n</code></pre>\n<h2>Case Sensitivity</h2>\n<p>Keywords, classes, functions, and user-defined functions are not case sensitive.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>But variables are.</li>\n</ul>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs language-html\"><span class=\"hljs-meta\">&#x3C;!DOCTYPE <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">html</span>></span>\n<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&#x3C;<span class=\"hljs-name\">html</span>></span>\n\n<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&#x3C;<span class=\"hljs-name\">body</span>></span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-meta\">&#x3C;?php\n        ECHO \"Hello world!&#x3C;br>\";\n        Echo \"Hello world!&#x3C;br>\";\n        echo \"Hello world!&#x3C;br>\";\n    ?></span>\n<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&#x3C;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">body</span>></span>\n\n<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&#x3C;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">html</span>></span>\n</code></pre>\n<p>Below represents the case-sensitivity of variables.</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs language-html\"><span class=\"hljs-meta\">&#x3C;!DOCTYPE <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">html</span>></span>\n<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&#x3C;<span class=\"hljs-name\">html</span>></span>\n\n<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&#x3C;<span class=\"hljs-name\">body</span>></span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-meta\">&#x3C;?php\n        $color = \"blue\";\n        echo \"My car is \" . $color . \"&#x3C;br>\";\n        echo \"My house is \" . $cOlOr . \"&#x3C;br>\";\n        echo \"My truck is \" . $Color . \"&#x3C;br>\";\n    ?></span>\n<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&#x3C;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">body</span>></span>\n\n<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&#x3C;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">html</span>></span>\n</code></pre>",
